Class Address

java.lang.Object
users.Address
Direct Known Subclasses:
BillingAddress, ShippingAddress
public abstract class Address extends Object
Abstract class representing a users address. This class contains address parameters such as (such as number, street, city, country, postCode, customerId, etc.) and provides methods for setting and getting address details. It also allows setting one address as the primary address for a customer and manages a list of address types.
